    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="card mx-auto" style="max-width: 600px;">
            <div class="card-body text-center">
                <img src="/images/tedx.png" alt="TEDxCUSAT" class="mb-4 tedx" width="200">
                <h1 class="card-title">Help</h1>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Need assistance? We're here to help! Find answers to common questions or get in touch with our support team.
                </p>
                <h2 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">FAQs</h2>
                <div class="text-left">
                    <h5>1. How do I register?</h5>
                    <p>To register, click on the "New User" button on the home page and fill in the required details.</p>
                    <h5>2. How do I log in?</h5>
                    <p>If you are a registered user, click on the "Registered User" button and enter your credentials.</p>
                    <h5>3. I forgot my password. What should I do?</h5>
                    <p>Click on the "Forgot Password" link on the login page and follow the instructions to reset your password.</p>
                    <h5>4. How can I update my profile?</h5>
                    <p>After logging in, go to the "Profile" section to update your details.</p>
                </div>
                <h2 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted mt-4">Contact Support</h2>
                <p class="card-text">
                    If you still need help, please reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:support@tedxcusat.com">support@tedxcusat.com</a>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

